This paper explores the design of an effective crowdsourcing system for an M-ary classification task, which involves human-computer interaction (HCI) and artificial intelligence (AI) techniques. Therefore, it is likely to belong to the Human-Computer Interaction (cs.HC), Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), Cybersecurity (cs.CY), Social and Information Networks (cs.SI), and Data Structures and Algorithms (cs.DS) sub-categories.
